---

💡 Why openrc still fails

Your openrc uses:

TERM=linux /opt/platform/.keyring/.../.CREDENTIAL

👉 But:

It does NOT use sudo

So it cannot decrypt password



---

🔥 Permanent Fix Option (Optional)

Edit openrc to use sudo:

sudo vi /etc/platform/openrc

Change:

export OS_PASSWORD=`TERM=linux /opt/platform/.keyring/.../.CREDENTIAL`

👉 To:

export OS_PASSWORD=`sudo /opt/platform/.keyring/.../.CREDENTIAL`


---

⚠️ Only do this if allowed by your environment policy.


